'From Squeak3.1alpha of 28 February 2001 [latest update: #4255] on 17 August 2001 at 5:03:32 pm'!"Change Set:		BorderProtocol-arDate:			17 August 2001Author:			Andreas RaabMove the border color protocol up to class morph."!!Morph methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ar 8/17/2001 16:51'!borderColor	^Color black! !!Morph methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ar 8/17/2001 16:51'!borderColor: aColor	"Ignored"! !!BorderedMorph methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ar 8/17/2001 16:52'!borderColor: colorOrSymbolOrNil	self doesBevels ifFalse:[		colorOrSymbolOrNil isColor ifFalse:[^self]].	borderColor = colorOrSymbolOrNil ifFalse: [		borderColor _ colorOrSymbolOrNil.		self changed].! !ProjectViewMorph removeSelector: #borderColor!ProjectViewMorph removeSelector: #borderColor:!ProjectViewMorph removeSelector: #borderWidth:!FlashPlayerMorph removeSelector: #borderWidth!FlashPlayerMorph removeSelector: #borderWidth:!